    Kinbit tree`
    ( ./kinbit_tree
    + typology
        ( genetic bit tree
            * kinbit tree
    + form
        - tree of waybits (kinbits) interlinked by kinbit links
    + function
        ( additional to surtype function
        - routes change flow
            - each link of the tree declares the mother waybit the default source for the flow
              of genetic content to the daughter
                - thence in turn to the daughter's daughters, if any, and so on
                - spreading leafward through the branches to all progeny
            - general effect
                - changes of genetic content propagate from progentitor to progeny
                  except where modified or stopped by other factors
                - mutatis mutandis, waybit copies tend to maintain a rough synchrony with their sources

